TransitionScene: {
	LoadingText: Data Linking...
	InitializingText: Initializing Protocols...
	Hint0: Do not ask why we kill the aberrations; ask instead why we do not.
	Hint1: The Acheron Protocol is one of Draedon's highest-level emergency contingencies.
	Hint2: Tactical Dolls know no fear, for fear itself is their weapon.
	Hint3: Draedon's mechanical creations have transcended the limits of reality.
	Hint4: No sacrifice is too great to be accepted, and no betrayal is too small to be forgiven.
	Hint5: Any sufficiently advanced technology is indistinguishable from magic.
	Hint6: Within the Calamity lies possibilities that transcend everything.
	Hint7: Draedon never acts without purpose; every step is the result of precise calculation.
	Hint8: Data is power, and knowledge is armament.
	Hint9: Machines do not betray, but those who control them might.
}

